title: Gary Gulman
description: One of Pete's earliest heros Gary Gulman (Last Comic Standing, HBO, comedy) came by to make it weird reminiscing about Boston, brothers who ruined his magic shows, and so much more. A supremely good episode! GET INTO IT WEIRDOS!!
